{"tid":1607901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周圍都係狗","createTime":"2019-10-01T05:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T06:01:27.000Z","uid":2733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"901d8773a5c9dc17e1684818c80fffa6f875bfb1","tid":1607901,"uid":2733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"調景嶺MTR同HlDI有狗，小心！"},{"pid":"63ce615c4012ddca5659e0d17ada3edd3a97c736","tid":1607901,"uid":2733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"901d8773a5c9dc17e1684818c80fffa6f875bfb1","tid":1607901,"uid":2733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"調景嶺MTR同HlDI有狗，小心！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"HKDI"},{"pid":"ff27ebdaddd8ee8d6ec35a8696c76f7264c13ad6","tid":1607901,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>我以颱風風眼橫過比喻，預測閱兵期間香港唔會發生衝突</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日警察不斷恐嚇大家聽日唔好出，同埋有很多假消息話各地暴徒會燒商場，呢個奇怪現象同早幾日批不反對通知書後立即大搜捕完全不同，<span style=\"color: red;\">就係因為警察知道，聽日唔可以捉人、唔可以出現血腥畫面，</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">但中共又唔容許有大量人上街反共反雜，所以先嚇定大家。<br />\n</span><br />\n現在就好似颱風風眼即將略過時候，警察瘋狂捉人，製造白色恐怖。<span style=\"color: red;\">風眼將會在明天閱兵期間橫過香港，忽然晴天萬里，到時候社會上一定太平無事，警察唔會拉人，大家可以放膽出街。</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">但要小心，當10月1日半夜過後，就有可能好似風眼過後，又出現狂風暴雨，</span>所以大家意見表達完結後，就盡快返歸，唔好戀戰。<br />\n<br />\n點解警察聽日閱兵期間唔捉人？<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令雜種即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責，</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日香港慘劇係雜種一手造成，冤有頭債有主，請大家對準政權目標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「天滅中共！習近平全家死」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f18c6f3d7c154480e972bba555e075707ddb7fe","tid":1607901,"uid":2733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"出去發夢要小心"},{"pid":"83fbd3cb4273a193940cdd2344342e45366d09cc","tid":1607901,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不流血不受傷不被捕</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6e5dcb4c2a26e60dc1bb3faef52fd2da51ddd61f","tid":1607901,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c8cc4b8b003ea33f5c3b1bbe2cd31c733f14041","tid":1607901,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"試著說xxx40防暴"},{"pid":"f532d9bc71e8f4fcd5f0af10d67ec0cf389c6677","tid":1607901,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"坑口A<br />\n約5隻無甲綠狗"},{"pid":"88157bf959e4f6042ba7926e02ca283522ac1af8","tid":1607901,"uid":2733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fVhq3K6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfVhq3K6.jpg&h=059df135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOFPLYu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOFPLYu.jpg&h=09ad30ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fo2q3Lb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffo2q3Lb.jpg&h=e630346a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56ed7e3f61d557dfda5e04e0fb47b229e1e63521","tid":1607901,"uid":2733,"like":0